page.title: 16Wetwang,Housing
page.content: There is all sorts of housing in Wetwang but no flats.Some of the houses are old and some are new. Many of the houses in the Main Street are old farmhouses and cottages that have been done up.Alot of them are partly built of chalk and they have tile roofs.Between them are some newer houses and bungalows. The houses in Northfield Road are newer and they are mainly occupied by older and retired people with a few families. Although Wetwang is a development area there is not much room in the north part of the village for any more houses.Much of the Main Street is a conservation area. In the rest of this area are some isolated farmhouses and farm cottages.
